      "settings": {
        "section_id": "wraps_accomdations",
        "heading": "ENJOY A TASTE OF HAWKE'S BAY WINE COUNTRY",
        "textfirst": "<p>On arrival at the Farmhouse, enjoy a complimentary bottle of Mission Estate Fête Brut Cuvée, grown and crafted on the winery premises.<br/><br/>Just a quick stroll through the vineyard takes you to Mission Estate Restaurant, open for lunch and dinner.</p>",
        "button_1_url": "shopify://pages/restaurant",
        "button_1_text": "Find out more",
        "button_2_url": "shopify://pages/restaurant",
        "button_2_text": "",
        "textsecond": "<p><strong>NOTES</strong></p><p>Two-night minimum stay. </p><p>No functions or parties unless agreed prior to the booking. </p><p>The Farmhouse standard nightly rate covers up to four guests. You can add two more guests when booking, for a total of six guests. Please ensure the number of guests matches your booking confirmation, unless you've made special arrangements with us ahead of your stay. </p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/accommodation-pic2.jpg",
